  "detailed_description": "<h1>Also recommended for you:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/66ac9011c0325278733f892a09ec4db1.avif?t=1642161472\" width=630 height=122 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/70a154bbec513c7e6a72c00301dfd861.poster.avif?t=1642161472\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/70a154bbec513c7e6a72c00301dfd861.webm?t=1642161472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/70a154bbec513c7e6a72c00301dfd861.mp4?t=1642161472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>Snowyland</strong> you should <strong>freeze</strong> a member of your family to <strong>create ice platforms</strong> that helps you to <strong>reach the meat</strong> at the end of the level. You can <strong>choose where</strong> the ice platform is placed, meaning that each player has an <strong>unique experience</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/cef5d776ee31bda025b820917ef2b646.poster.avif?t=1642161472\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/cef5d776ee31bda025b820917ef2b646.webm?t=1642161472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/cef5d776ee31bda025b820917ef2b646.mp4?t=1642161472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Many Levels</strong> - Snowyland has more than 45 levels, your family must explore and find  new ingredients for your dinner.<br><br></li><li> <strong>Alternative Paths</strong> - Certain levels allow for a varied solution, it's up to you to decide the number of sacrifices.<br><br></li><li> <strong>Hidden Items</strong> - Find hidden vegetables around the levels to make your dinner even more delicious!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731730/extras/7d339a46b2e82842c102cd6d5144f194.avif?t=1642161472\" width=600 height=124 /></span>",
